game.name: Go Runner Go
game.description:
Have you got bored trying out games with boring adventure themes? Do you want to explore a completely unique and funny adventurous story? Then join Go Runner Go right away to give your gaming senses an ultimate treat! In this brand new adventure game, you have to help a boy to run as far as possible to complete his adventure-filled trip. The game includes several complex obstacles to make your gaming experience quite interesting and engaging. 

Your goal is to help this brave boy reach the portals to pass to a completely new world through difficult obstacles and tests. After helping him to reach the last world, you also have to take care of taking him to the chest to ensure your win in the end. Try to focus on the screen while changing one platform to another in this free online highly addictive game! Several platforms are moving, so wait and make a jump when it comes near to you. 

There are also obstacles like hazardous wolves and problems-filled path to restrict you from achieving your mission. Make sure to collect as many coins as possible to improve your score in this cool HTML5 game. The incredibly responsive controls and improved graphics are enough to keep you engaged for hours. Keep running while completing the missions and gaining the achievements in this cute jumping game!
